name: Sunset Sky Deepest Dream
description: Did you ever see a sunset so good it took over your dreams? - We are nature, nature is us. All technology has stemmed from human advances and creativity. Humans are the originators of this computer driven technology and without humans arising from nature it all would not exist. Is this technology then natural?  Through my work using nature as a focus I am examining the interplay between both the natural and the digital and exploring the dance between the two. @PrimaryNature
